room_title: Escape room "Lab Disaster" by Epic Escape Game in Denver
room_address: 9600 E. Arapahoe Road, Suite 212, Greenwood Village, CO 80112
room_description: Labcon is the world's largest maker of laughing gas. A malfunction in the engine room initiated a building lockdown and is now causing the laughing gas to leak into the lab. Your only hope is to get into the engine room and shut off the main control panel. Hurry, you only have one hour before your oxygen runs out...
